Modifications made in this repository include, but are not limited to:
  - Target task changed to agent/tool-calling routing, evaluated on
    BFCL v4 (Berkeley Function Calling Leaderboard).
  - Model pair changed to Qwen3.5 models (e.g. 0.8B / 2B weak vs 9B strong).
  - Query embeddings replaced with local intfloat/multilingual-e5-* models
    (no external embedding API).
  - Added routers: UniRoute cluster-based router and a per-model regression
    router (R2-Router skeleton, budget-free).
  - Added BFCL data preparation, model evaluation, analysis, and reporting
    tooling.

